data.description: $5,000 grant available!!! Additional items within the house can be included in the sale with the right offer. Nestled in the heart of York City, this captivating property offers spacious living with four bedrooms and one and a half bathrooms. What sets this home apart is the inclusion of an additional adjoining lot, expanding the property to a generous 0.28-acre, creating ample outdoor space for your enjoyment. Furthermore, the convenience of six parking spots ensures that both you and your guests will have plenty of room to accommodate vehicles.  The features of this house make it a standout choice for those who love to entertain or have a large family. You'll find laundry hookups on the first floor for added convenience, a beautiful kitchen with granite countertops and an exquisite backsplash, as well as a fully fenced yard, offering privacy and security. With these attributes and more, this property is ideal for those seeking both comfort and accessibility in York City. It's the perfect blend of spacious living, a substantial lot, and ample parking options, all within a vibrant urban setting. Come see it today!!!
